reviews.review_text: 1st Dead show I was so amazed when my friend Patti turned me on to this site.  On Christmas night in 82 another friend gave me a ticket to the  following night's show.  (Needless to say I was hooked.)  28 years later I'm hearing that show for the first time since 82 and I have the biggest smile on my face.  That has got to be one of the hottest Estimated/ Eyes I have ever heard.  Thanks to the tapers and thanks for this wonderful site.
- Starts out great, then they rush China/Rider and it it gets a bit sloppy from there...
